                            <comment id="17020859" author="krummas" created="Wed, 22 Jan 2020 07:45:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1, nits;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;the comment in the &lt;tt&gt;RepairedDataPurger&lt;/tt&gt; constructor should be removed (&lt;tt&gt;isForThrift&lt;/tt&gt; is gone in 4.0)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;WithTracking&lt;/tt&gt; - keep the &lt;tt&gt;protected DecoratedKey applyToPartitionKey(DecoratedKey key)&lt;/tt&gt; method and call &lt;tt&gt;repairedDataInfo.onNewPartition(iterator);&lt;/tt&gt; there?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
